Background




Pilnick, Gary H. was born on September 17, 1964 in Forest Hills, New York, United States.
					
					



Education


	 		
			

			Graduate, Lafayette College, 1986. Law degree with honors, Duke University, 1989.
			
       			












Career


	 		
			Attorney Jenner and Block, Chicago, 1989—1995. Vice president, chief Corporate Counsel Specialty Foods Corporation, 1995—1997. Chief counsel corporation development and finance Sara Lee Corporation, 1997—1999.Vice president, chief counsel Sara Lee Branded Apparel, 1999—2000. Vice president, deputy general counsel, assistant secretary Kellogg Company, 2000—2003, senior  vice president, general counsel corporation development, secretary, since 2003.
			
       			













