Insider Activity


Individual




Gary H. Pilnick



Mr. Gary H. Pilnick is Vice Chairman & Chief Legal Officer at Kellogg Co. He is on the Board of Directors at Kellogg Co. and Irving S. Gilmore International Keyboard Festival. Mr. Pilnick was previously employed as Chief Counsel & Vice President by Sara Lee Branded Apparel, Chief Corporate Counsel & Vice President by Specialty Foods Corp., and Chief Counsel & VP-Finance & Corporate Development by The Hillshire Brands Co. He received his undergraduate degree from Lafayette College and a graduate degree from Duke University School of Law.



